# WatermelonDB Patterns

## Schema Definition

```ts
import { appSchema, tableSchema } from '@nozbe/watermelondb';

export default appSchema({
  version: 1,
  tables: [
    tableSchema({
      name: 'transactions',
      columns: [
        { name: 'amount', type: 'number' },
        { name: 'currency', type: 'string' },
        { name: 'wallet_id', type: 'string', isIndexed: true },
        { name: 'category_id', type: 'string', isIndexed: true },
        { name: 'created_at', type: 'number' },
        { name: 'updated_at', type: 'number' },
      ],
    }),
  ],
});
```

## Model Definition

```ts
import { Model } from '@nozbe/watermelondb';
import { field, date, relation, readonly } from '@nozbe/watermelondb/decorators';

export default class TransactionModel extends Model {
  static table = 'transactions';
  static associations = {
    wallets: { type: 'belongs_to' as const, key: 'wallet_id' },
    categories: { type: 'belongs_to' as const, key: 'category_id' },
  };

  @field('amount') amount!: number;
  @field('currency') currency!: string;
  @relation('wallets', 'wallet_id') wallet!: any;
  @readonly @date('created_at') createdAt!: Date;
  @readonly @date('updated_at') updatedAt!: Date;
}
```

## Clean Architecture Integration

- DB Models live in `src/data/database/models/` (data layer)
- Domain entities live in `src/domain/entities/` (domain layer, no DB dependency)
- Mappers in `src/data/mappers/` convert between Model and Entity
- Repositories in `src/data/repositories/` implement domain interfaces using DB queries

## Rules

- Always wrap writes in `database.write(async () => { ... })`
- Use `database.batch(...)` for multiple operations in one transaction
- Column names use `snake_case`, model properties use `camelCase`
- Always add `isIndexed: true` to foreign key columns and frequently queried columns
- Use `Q.where`, `Q.and`, `Q.or`, `Q.sortBy` for queries; never filter in JS
- Increment schema version + add migration for every schema change
- Use `@readonly @date` decorators for timestamp fields
- Export database instance from `src/data/database/index.ts`
- Write tests for all repository implementations
